i\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">switch JC手柄 R键维修</span><br><span class=\"line\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1E441117gM/</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Switch Joy Con R按钮易损坏的通病原因及预防修理，如不及时修补，会导致主板焊盘脱落</span><br><span class=\"line\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?<span class=\"attr\">v</span>=pZBNbJe8bU4</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">修复R键主板焊盘全部脱落的任天堂Switch Joy Con手柄</span><br><span class=\"line\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?<span class=\"attr\">v</span>=p0ke8SoCMeE</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 这里有检测微动是否损坏的测量方法</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">熊孩子暴力摔switch 手柄joycon后的 R键修复记</span><br><span class=\"line\">https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwgpd6x/</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">不花钱，修好switch joy con右手柄R键，微动碎裂，焊盘脱落</span><br><span class=\"line\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Ak4y1t7qz/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"灵感来源\"><a href=\"#灵感来源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"灵感来源\"></a>灵感来源</h1><p><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Ti4y1T7u3/\">羊羹爸爸 尝试维修5块Switch Joy Con故障主板，能修好几块呐？</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1S94y127PR\">switch 手柄无反应 灯不亮 不能充电 连接不上</a></p>","categories":[{"name":"switch","path":"api/categories/switch.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"switch","path":"api/tags/switch.json"}]}